      <Section id="tools" title="Scale Path & Tooling" themeTag="Tools">

        <Technique id="t8" title="8. Scale Breakpoints — Khi nào cần gì" tid="8" location="LLM Wiki v2 — Implementation spectrum">
          <Subheading level="h4" text="Scale breakpoints" />
          <Diagram>{`
0–50 pages: index.md đủ tốt
  → LLM đọc toàn bộ index trong 1 pass (<10K tokens)
  → Không cần gì thêm

50–200 pages: index.md + structured format
  → Add confidence scores, typed relationships
  → LLM đọc index + drill into relevant pages
  → Vẫn không cần search infra

200–500 pages: BM25
  → index.md quá dài để read in 1 pass
  → Add BM25 index (whoosh hoặc rank-bm25)
  → LLM query BM25 → get top-10 → read those pages

500–2000 pages: BM25 + Vector
  → BM25 misses semantic matches
  → Add vector index (FAISS + sentence-transformers)
  → Hybrid search với simple score fusion

2000+ pages: Full hybrid (BM25 + Vector + Graph)
  → Graph traversal essential cho complex queries
  → RRF fusion
  → Consider hosted solution (Weaviate, Qdrant, Pinecone)
          `}</Diagram>
        </Technique>

